item.title: Consultancy
item.description: Buying a house can be stressful, and there are a lot of costs throughout the buying process. These costs add up, and if you invest in the wrong house it can be hard to recover from the loses. The best way you can lower your chances of making a bad investment is to research the house beforehand. We are here to make that process easier. Our services are provided at a flat rate of $300 and include a report on the house and the neighborhood.
